{"tid":881562,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"頂，得返一個腎，你想我點啊！！！","createTime":"2018-10-29T14:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T01:30:55.000Z","uid":219232,"like":10,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"04760221ec6325feae4b09b2b8d679d612e19c39","tid":881562,"uid":219232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:03:03.000Z","msg":"Apple 2018第二場發佈會（ 開定先 推到完場）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<strong><em>以下係關於發佈會的消息：</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95EP3m5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95EP3m5.png&h=044e461b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F31nDVD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF31nDVD.png&h=9d0b1504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於 iPad Pro<br />\n<br />\n新款 iPad Pro 是 2015 年問世以來最重大的更新：<br />\n<br />\n採用全螢幕設計，超窄、對稱邊框，類似最新款 iPhone。<br />\n採用 USB-C 連接埠用於充電和傳輸數據，是 iOS 裝置首次採用該充電標準。<br />\n採用 Face ID 解鎖，移除主螢幕按鈕和指紋辨識功能，Face ID 支援橫直向辨識。<br />\n支援 Emoji / Animoji。<br />\n採用 LCD 螢幕，不是 iPhone X 系列的 OLED 螢幕。<br />\n外觀經過重新設計，更方正，類似 iPhone 5、5s 和 iPhone SE。<br />\nA12 仿生晶片的變種晶片。<br />\n蘋果自研圖形晶片，iPad 史上首次。<br />\n新款 Apple Pencil。<br />\n<br />\n關於 Mac<br />\n<br />\n自 2017 年 6 月以來首次大範圍更新 Mac 產品線，消息人士稱以下產品可能會在下週發表：<br />\n<br />\n全新入門級筆電取代 MacBook Air，採用更高解析度的 13 吋螢幕，超窄邊框設計。<br />\n自 2014 年首次更新 Mac mini，配置全新處理器及為專業用戶準備的功能。<br />\n蘋果還打算更新 iMac、iMac Pro 及 12 吋 MacBook，其中有些可能會在下週發表。<br />\n<br />\n紐約布魯克林音樂學院已準備就緒，我們拭目以待吧。<br />\n<br />\n資料來自<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2018/10/29/new-ipad-pro-macbook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2018%2F10%2F29%2Fnew-ipad-pro-macbook%2F&d=w1DYE0FbBOdQUunHkjbyZDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b5a949a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2018/10/29/new-ipad-pro-macbook/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家比較期待聽晚邊樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> New MacBook Air<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> New iPad Pro</span></strong>"},{"pid":"68b32296939036afb467f88dcbb971d07cd25c3c","tid":881562,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"LM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42295815b39e6f4a7c780872c2db80d4b253218f","tid":881562,"uid":7763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:05:02.000Z","msg":"全螢幕ipad<br />\n一定買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a7fb50087d41c825642f36ca5d7d61cf7ff4c1","tid":881562,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:23:08.000Z","msg":"mac mini"},{"pid":"3d1f5cdfd28a6936e884e1a971367724ffcb44df","tid":881562,"uid":166377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:16:56.000Z","msg":"USB-C<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1168e58b06e6af8df143724e81be202d406f48","tid":881562,"uid":32570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:30:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Apple 2018第二場發佈會（ 開定先 推到完場）<br />\n<img src=\"/